{
  "id": "6a413e841b6d6dddb3134d4f",
  "title": "graspを試す(inajob)",
  "created": 1782660742,
  "updated": 1782661696,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a413e841b6d6dddb3134d4f",
      "text": "graspを試す(inajob)",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660742,
      "updated": 1782660745
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4140360000000000cea590",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661175,
      "updated": 1782661175
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413e8a0000000000cea582",
      "text": "\t[grasp]を試す",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660746,
      "updated": 1782660768
    },
    {
      "id": "6a41422d0000000000cea593",
      "text": "\t非井戸端adminで OpenCodeをつかって無料で試す方法をメモ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661678,
      "updated": 1782661696
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413e9f0000000000cea584",
      "text": "\t[GitHub Actionsで井戸端プロジェクトのバックアップを取得しReleaseに登録する]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660768,
      "updated": 1782660804
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413ed20000000000cea586",
      "text": " \thttps://github.com/meganii/sandbox-github-actions-scheduler/releases/tag/2026-06-28 などにあるdata.zipの中にあるdata.jsonが井戸端のexport json",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660819,
      "updated": 1782661182
    },
    {
      "id": "6a4140400000000000cea592",
      "text": " \t\tadminじゃないとCosenseのProsjectSettingsからはexport出来ないが、この方法ならだれでも利用できる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661185,
      "updated": 1782661666
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413ec10000000000cea585",
      "text": "\t$ git clone git@github.com:nishio/grasp.git",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660802,
      "updated": 1782660871
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413f040000000000cea588",
      "text": "\t$ pip install -e .",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660869,
      "updated": 1782660893
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413f330000000000cea58a",
      "text": "\t$ python3 -m grasp import --cosense ~/Downloads/data/data/data.json",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660915,
      "updated": 1782660916
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413f1c0000000000cea589",
      "text": "\tOpenCodeから使いたいので、skillをopencodeのconfigに追加",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782660892,
      "updated": 1782661038
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413fad0000000000cea58c",
      "text": "\t\t$ cp -r skills/grasp ~/.config/opencode/skills/",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661038,
      "updated": 1782661065
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413f960000000000cea58b",
      "text": "\t> inajobについて何を書いた？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661016,
      "updated": 1782661099
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413fe90000000000cea58d",
      "text": "\t\tで、graspを使い井戸端のデータからinajobのことを出力してくれた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661097,
      "updated": 1782661113
    },
    {
      "id": "6a413fee0000000000cea58e",
      "text": "\tBig Pickle というモデルがどの程度賢いのかわからず使っている・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661103,
      "updated": 1782661243
    },
    {
      "id": "6a41401d0000000000cea58f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1782661150,
      "updated": 1782661150
    }
  ]
}